- [x] T017 [P] Write unit test for single row read in tests/csv_engine_test.rs verifying correct field parsing at any offset
- [x] T018 [P] Write unit test for in-place write (same length) in tests/csv_engine_test.rs
- [x] T019 [P] Write unit test for in-place write (different length) in tests/csv_engine_test.rs verifying tail-shift strategy
- [x] T020 [P] Write unit test for quoted CSV fields in tests/csv_engine_test.rs (fields with commas, newlines, quotes)
